name: Aabha Corporation
overview:
Incorporated in year 2009, we, “Aabha Corporation”, are a trustworthy organization engaged in manufacturing, supplying, exporting and trading a commendable assortment of Bamboo Furniture, Hand Cleaner and Food Product.

Products: Square Dining Table Set Wooden Stool Wooden Table Arm Chair Master Bed Bamboo Cabinet Shelf Outdoor Bamboo Furniture Hand Cleaner Food Product

Our Team: We are backed by a team of highly qualified and passionate professionals, who are appointed after stringent short listing procedures on the basis of their qualifications, knowledge.

Our Infrastructure: To cater to the bulk requirements of our esteemed clients, we have constructed a sophisticated infrastructure facility.

Our Quality: Being a quality conscious organization, we are committed towards offering a quality-approved range of Bamboo Furniture, Hand Cleaner and Food Product.

Client Satisfaction: In order to achieve maximum client satisfaction, we work with one focus to offer a quality assured range of Bamboo Furniture, Hand Cleaner and Food Product.
